== Histogram GUI ==

Provide a GUI in which users can view histograms and manipulate plots

 * make plots for 1D/2D histograms
 * display info and meta data of a histogram
 * manipulate histograms in a python shell window so we can create slices, projections, etc
 * simple manipulation of plots
   * change plot title
   * change axis labels
   * select region of plot
   * choose ticks / add minor ticks
   * change color coding
   * choose color palette
   * error bar on/off
   * *add colorbar*
